SELECT mda.moh_age_group AS age_group, gender, COUNT(a.client_id)
FROM mamba_fact_encounter_hiv_art_summary a
         LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM mamba_fact_transfer_in WHERE transfer_in_date BETWEEN ':startDate' AND ':endDate') b
                   ON a.client_id = b.client_id
         INNER JOIN mamba_fact_patients_latest_patient_demographics mdp ON a.client_id = mdp.patient_id
         LEFT JOIN mamba_dim_agegroup mda ON mda.age = mdp.age
WHERE encounter_datetime BETWEEN ':startDate' AND ':endDate'
  AND b.client_id IS NULL
GROUP BY age_group, gender

SELECT mda.moh_age_group AS age_group, gender, COUNT(a.client_id)
FROM mamba_fact_encounter_hiv_art_summary a
         LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM mamba_fact_transfer_in WHERE transfer_in_date BETWEEN ':startDate' AND ':endDate') b

         INNER JOIN mamba_fact_patients_latest_patient_demographics mdp ON a.client_id = mdp.patient_id
         LEFT JOIN mamba_dim_agegroup mda ON mda.age = mdp.age
WHERE encounter_datetime BETWEEN ':startDate' AND ':endDate' and entry_point_into_hiv_care='PMTCT'

GROUP BY age_group, gender;

SELECT mda.moh_age_group AS age_group, gender, COUNT(a.client_id)
FROM mamba_fact_encounter_hiv_art_summary a
         LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM mamba_fact_transfer_in WHERE transfer_in_date BETWEEN ':startDate' AND ':endDate') b
                   ON a.client_id = b.client_id
         INNER JOIN mamba_fact_patients_latest_patient_demographics mdp ON a.client_id = mdp.patient_id
         INNER JOIN mamba_fact_encounter_hiv_art_card mfehac on mfehac.client_id = a.client_id
         LEFT JOIN mamba_dim_agegroup mda ON mda.age = mdp.age
WHERE encounter_datetime BETWEEN ':startDate' AND ':endDate'
  AND mfehac.encounter_date BETWEEN ':startDate' AND ':endDate'
  AND tuberculosis_status is not null
  AND b.client_id IS NULL
GROUP BY age_group, gender;

SELECT mda.moh_age_group AS age_group, gender, COUNT(a.client_id)
FROM mamba_fact_encounter_hiv_art_summary a
         LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM mamba_fact_transfer_in WHERE transfer_in_date BETWEEN ':startDate' AND ':endDate') b
                   ON a.client_id = b.client_id
         INNER JOIN mamba_fact_patients_latest_patient_demographics mdp ON a.client_id = mdp.patient_id
         INNER JOIN mamba_fact_encounter_hiv_art_card mfehac on mfehac.client_id = a.client_id
         LEFT JOIN mamba_dim_agegroup mda ON mda.age = mdp.age
WHERE encounter_datetime BETWEEN ':startDate' AND ':endDate'
  AND mfehac.encounter_date BETWEEN ':startDate' AND ':endDate'
  AND (tuberculosis_status like '%Diagnosed%' or tuberculosis_status = 'Currently on TB treatment')
  AND b.client_id IS NULL
GROUP BY age_group, gender;

SELECT mda.moh_age_group AS age_group, gender, COUNT( DISTINCT mfehac.client_id) from
                  mamba_fact_encounter_hiv_art_card mfehac
                 INNER JOIN mamba_fact_patients_latest_patient_demographics mdp ON mfehac.client_id = mdp.patient_id
                 LEFT JOIN mamba_dim_agegroup mda ON mda.age = mdp.age
              where mfehac.crag_test_results like '%positive%'
AND mfehac.encounter_date BETWEEN ':startDate' AND ':endDate'
GROUP BY age_group, gender;

SELECT mda.moh_age_group AS age_group, gender, COUNT(DISTINCT mfehac.client_id)
FROM mamba_fact_encounter_hiv_art_card mfehac
    INNER JOIN mamba_fact_encounter_hiv_art_card b on b.client_id=mfehac.client_id
         INNER JOIN mamba_fact_patients_latest_patient_demographics mdp ON mfehac.client_id = mdp.patient_id
         LEFT JOIN mamba_dim_agegroup mda ON mda.age = mdp.age
WHERE mfehac.tuberculosis_status = 'TB Diagnosed - TB LAM'
  AND b.tuberculosis_treatment_start_date BETWEEN ':startDate' AND ':endDate'
  AND mfehac.encounter_date BETWEEN ':startDate' AND ':endDate'
GROUP BY age_group, gender;

SELECT mda.moh_age_group AS age_group, gender, COUNT( DISTINCT  mfehac.client_id) from

SELECT mda.moh_age_group AS age_group, gender, COUNT(DISTINCT mfehas.client_id)
FROM mamba_fact_encounter_hiv_art_summary mfehas
         INNER JOIN mamba_fact_patients_latest_patient_demographics mdp ON mfehas.client_id = mdp.patient_id
         LEFT JOIN mamba_dim_agegroup mda ON mda.age = mdp.age
WHERE date_positive_hiv_test_confirmed >= ':startDate'
  AND date_positive_hiv_test_confirmed <= ':endDate'
  AND baseline_regimen_start_date >= ':startDate'
  AND baseline_regimen_start_date <= ':endDate'
GROUP BY age_group, gender;

SELECT mda.moh_age_group AS age_group, gender, COUNT(DISTINCT mfehas.client_id)
FROM mamba_fact_encounter_hiv_art_summary mfehas
         INNER JOIN mamba_fact_patients_latest_patient_demographics mdp ON mfehas.client_id = mdp.patient_id
         LEFT JOIN mamba_dim_agegroup mda ON mda.age = mdp.age
         LEFT JOIN (SELECT client_id
                    FROM mamba_fact_transfer_in
                    WHERE transfer_in_date >= ':startDate' AND transfer_in_date <= ':endDate') mfti ON
    mfti.client_id = mfehas.client_id
WHERE baseline_regimen_start_date >= ':startDate'
  AND baseline_regimen_start_date <= ':endDate'
  AND mfti.client_id IS NULL
GROUP BY age_group, gender;
